creator: Harriet Beecher Stowe
description:
LibriVox recording of Queer Little Folks by Harriet Beecher Stowe.
Read in English by Claire Schreuder; Larry Greene; Deena Rhoads; Jennifer Dorr; Pam Castille
A wonderful children's classic - a collection of moral stories told by animals in the woods. The wittily written stories explore various issues in a fun way. - Summary by Claire Schreuder
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
